mdElement.text: Wired force sensor used for ground truth measurements

The Workcell block is purely conceptual. Realization using the blocks within this model should be created using a new block not defined within this model. Examples include the Industrial Wireless Systems Testbed (IWS_Testbed) package included within this project.
Includes security, configuration, management, synchronization, etc. i.e. services described by the IWN specification
